  "prompt": "What is the meaning of Hindi word \u2018\u092d\u0947\u0926\u092d\u093e\u0935\u2019 (Bhedbhaav)?",
  "response": "The Hindi word \u2018\u092d\u0947\u0926\u092d\u093e\u0935\u2019 (Bhedbhaav) translates to \"discrimination\" or \"distinction\" in English. It refers to the act of making a difference in treatment or consideration based on certain characteristics, often in a negative or unfair manner. For example, discrimination based on race, gender, or caste can be referred to as \u2018\u092d\u0947\u0926\u092d\u093e\u0935\u2019.",
